{"tid":1019350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盧醫牲倡港人可輪候內地捐贈器官　港深醫院集中處理移植手術","createTime":"2019-02-13T01:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T18:21:42.000Z","uid":83052,"like":2,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"96a156ff269b218b30d7d8ea113ea8b197440445","tid":1019350,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T01:15:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/293656/%E7%9B%A7%E5%AF%B5%E8%8C%82%E5%80%A1%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%AF%E8%BC%AA%E5%80%99%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%8D%90%E8%B4%88%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98-%E6%B8%AF%E6%B7%B1%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E7%A7%BB%E6%A4%8D%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F293656%2F%25E7%259B%25A7%25E5%25AF%25B5%25E8%258C%2582%25E5%2580%25A1%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%258D%2590%25E8%25B4%2588%25E5%2599%25A8%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%259B%2586%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25A4%258D%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25A1%2593&d=IVQfIEXj%2BCIGzEn528CwiVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=3b02b4e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/293656/%E7%9B%A7%E5%AF%B5%E8%8C%82%E5%80%A1%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%AF%E8%BC%AA%E5%80%99%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%8D%90%E8%B4%88%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98-%E6%B8%AF%E6%B7%B1%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E7%A7%BB%E6%A4%8D%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93</a><br />\n<br />\n盧寵茂指，本港去年肝移植手術不足60宗，數字較以往少，而內地去年有超過6000宗器官移植，而且器官捐贈者不再只是死囚，捐贈者都為自願，形容內地有資源。他稱港人亦可接受內地的器官捐贈，每年香港都有數十人到內地尋找器官捐贈者，因分散各地，不便港人，「有人整個家庭到上海住1、2個月等待，很大壓力。」<br />\n<br />\n盧寵茂建議，港府可與內地政府商討，特設讓港人輪候的內地器官捐贈輪候冊，或集中把所有港人器官移植手術在港深醫院進行，可更便利亦有助保證質素。<br />\n<br />\n不過，港深醫院需在2年內有10個器官捐贈者，才能申領做器官移植手術的牌照，盧指會繼續進行有關工作。<br />\n<br />\n另外，港大醫學院院長梁卓偉今在傳媒茶聚上，送出一款豬型圖案的紀念幣予傳媒，豬型圖案上特別描繪了心和肝的圖案，梁笑指除代表「有心肝」，亦為鼓勵器官捐贈，而背後的DNA圖案，就為表示希望日後人類可透過科技，去創造器官治療疾病。"},{"pid":"2589db047c65550dd139ba068fe8d983b5e04c3f","tid":1019350,"uid":83052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T01:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afaa98b26c37a3e8464d99fa43df521bed0b254f","tid":1019350,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T02:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cfc4297937af37f7de66594fafc10c0635612dd","tid":1019350,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T02:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1d9337872599c3e45ff27994cc795510a9beb9","tid":1019350,"uid":148332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:43:53.000Z","msg":"腳傷好番未?"},{"pid":"ced7b678050749b02970c87ba7e2f94048f9dc97","tid":1019350,"uid":6946,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:45:30.000Z","msg":"限返d新移民要排大陸隊好撚過啦"},{"pid":"a838e9dcf85d94d12d6b25a53bd921b577aa18ae","tid":1019350,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T07:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551f94e97c74e91d727bfb8dfca107a04f7d77d0","tid":1019350,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T07:55:20.000Z","msg":"讓領導先捐"},{"pid":"2a5e399d4d2f51ce8ab0edffc58ddaf13d10641c","tid":1019350,"uid":119864,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T02:45:17.000Z","msg":"依加話大陸捐俾香港，下次會唔會香港捐番去大陸<br />\n<br />\n所有政府一步一步向大陸接軌"},{"pid":"fbc1ffa2e01eaa4333ff95f060c25fee8d9ea697","tid":1019350,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a5e399d4d2f51ce8ab0edffc58ddaf13d10641c","tid":1019350,"uid":119864,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"re